text.section:
This section does not apply to the following if operated intrastate only:
Vehicles registered as:
Farm trucks under § 13-921 of this article;
Farm truck tractors under § 13-924 of this article; or
Farm area motor vehicles under § 13-935 of this article;
Trucks registered at 10,000 pounds capacity or less;
Emergency vehicles;
Vehicles used primarily to transport money or commercial paper;
Vehicles owned or operated by the State or any political subdivision of the State; or
Vehicles operating within 15 days from the date of purchase.
